I along with my gang were here for dinner.

The name‚Äù Punjabi ‚Äú pulled us to this restaurant

We ordered paneer handi, egg curry, chicken biryani , daal fry, butter roti and cheeze balls.

To our disappointment, we found that there is nothing punjabi in the taste of the food.

Except egg curry everything else was not up to the mark. The taste was really bad

Please do not visit this restaurant if you really care about how your food tastes

The location of the food place makes it very attractive. Great food options at reasonable. Good quality food and great service from the staff. Very efficient and attentive staff.

It's worth the visit. It is great for families and friends to hang out at the location. Good location.

description:
### Punjabi Kitchen Bar & Restaurant: A Culinary Journey in Calangute, Goa

Nestled in the vibrant coastal town of Calangute, Goa, **Punjabi Kitchen Bar & Restaurant** stands out with an impressive **4.7-star rating** based on **7,662 reviews**. Guests are drawn to this eatery not only for its promise of authentic North Indian food but also for its inviting atmosphere, making it a notable destination for seafood lovers and those craving comfort classics like **aloo paratha** and more.

#### Ambiance & Design
As you step into Punjabi Kitchen Bar & Restaurant, you are immediately struck by the bright and lively d√©cor that captures the essence of a traditional Punjabi dining experience. The establishment features colorful wall art and warm lighting that creates a welcoming environment. The open layout allows for ample space, making it perfect for families and groups of friends looking to enjoy a meal together. From the ambiance described in photos, we can see rustic wooden furniture juxtaposed with vibrant decorations that reflect the rich culture of Punjab.

#### Menu & Culinary Experience
The menu at Punjabi Kitchen offers a diverse array of dishes, showcasing both vegetarian and non-vegetarian options. Signature items such as **paneer handi**, **chicken biryani**, and the **deluxe thalis** have garnered substantial attention. One enthusiastic reviewer highlighted the **veg manchurian** and **naan** as particularly noteworthy, praising their generous portions and great flavors. However, there were mixed feelings about certain dishes, with some patrons feeling the need for more authenticity in the Punjabi flavors. The emphasis on fresh ingredients and generous serving sizes is a recurring theme, making it a satisfying option for hungry diners.

The restaurant also provides a selection of drinks, adding to the overall culinary experience, and ensuring that there is something for everyone, whether you‚Äôre looking to indulge in a hearty meal or just relax with beverages in hand.

#### Customer Experience & Service
The reviews paint a picture of a team that is both **efficient** and **attentive**, enhancing the overall dining experience. Guests have noted the friendly demeanor of the staff, who seem eager to ensure that everyone enjoys their meal. Whether you‚Äôre a first-time visitor or a returning customer, you can expect a warm welcome. Suggestions from the reviews indicate it‚Äôs worthwhile to call ahead for reservations, particularly during peak tourist seasons when Calangute buzzes with activity.

#### Popularity & Reviews
The popularity of Punjabi Kitchen Bar & Restaurant is furthered by its strategic location, making it an attractive option for both locals and tourists. Many reviews commend the reasonable pricing, and the establishment has become a buzzworthy spot on social media for those seeking authentic Northern Indian dishes framed in a family-friendly atmosphere. While some critiques mention inconsistencies in flavor‚Äîpointing out that not all dishes capture the Punjabi spirit‚Äîmany still urge visitors to give it a try, confirming that the experience can be delightful.

#### Utilizing Visual Content
Customer-generated photos serve to amplify the positive attributes of Punjabi Kitchen. Images display beautifully plated dishes that entice the viewer, from steaming bowls of vibrant curries to decadent thalis filled to the brim with choice delicacies. The contrast of the rich colors of the food against the warm, lively backdrop of the restaurant makes for an appealing visual narrative that excites potential diners.

In conclusion, **Punjabi Kitchen Bar & Restaurant** offers a charming setting, a diverse menu, and a level of service that makes it a worthy stop for anyone seeking to experience the flavors of Punjab amidst the scenic beauty of Goa. With mixed reviews regarding authenticity, those who enter with an open mind may just find a favorite dish‚Äîpairing great food with the warmth of Goan hospitality.
